                </div>
            </div>


            <div class="w-2/3 flex flex-col justify-between">

                <p class="text-gray-800 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    Mr. Pandey's persistent knee pain was relieved after a successful
                    partial knee replacement surgery by Dr. Harish Ghoota-Director of
                    Orthopaedics at Fortis Escorts Hospital. Now, he's active and pain-free,
                    thanks to Dr. Ghoota's expertise and the hospital's dedicated team.
                </p>

                <div class="mt-8 text-gray-500 text-sm">
                    Jeevan Jyoti Hospital
                </div>

                <div class="self-end text-[80px] leading-none text-[#e6c7bb] font-serif">
                    ”
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>


    </div>

    </div>

    <footer class="bg-slate-900 text-gray-300 pt-12 pb-6 mt-20">

        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-10">


            <div>
                <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-hospital"></i> Jeevan Jyoti Hospital
                </h2>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Providing trusted healthcare services with advanced medical technology,
                    compassionate doctors, and patient-first care.
                </p>
            </div>


            <div>
                <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4">Quick Links</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white">About Us</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white">Departments</a></li>
